```mermaid
%% AgriOps — Authentication Flow (Phase 2)
sequenceDiagram

    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Django
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Axes as django-axes

    %% ─────────────────────────────────────
    %% LOGIN FLOW
    %% ─────────────────────────────────────

    User->>Browser: Navigate to /login/
    Browser->>Django: GET /login/
    Django-->>Browser: Render login page (styled template)

    User->>Browser: Submit username + password
    Browser->>Django: POST /login/ {username, password}

    Django->>Axes: Check brute-force lockout status for IP/username
    Axes-->>Django: Not locked

    Django->>DB: SELECT CustomUser WHERE username=?
    DB-->>Django: User record

    Django->>Django: Validate password hash (bcrypt)

    alt Credentials valid
        Django->>DB: UPDATE last_login
        Django->>Django: Create session / issue JWT (Phase 2: JWT)
        Django->>DB: INSERT AuditLog {action: login, user, ip}
        Django-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to dashboard
        Browser->>Django: GET /
        Django-->>Browser: Render dashboard
    else Credentials invalid
        Django->>Axes: Record failed attempt {ip, username}
        Axes->>Axes: Increment failure counter
        alt Failure threshold reached
            Axes-->>Django: Account/IP locked
            Django-->>Browser: 403 Account locked message
        else Under threshold
            Django-->>Browser: 200 Login page with error message
        end
    end

    %% ─────────────────────────────────────
    %% AUTHENTICATED REQUEST FLOW
    %% ─────────────────────────────────────

    User->>Browser: Navigate to /suppliers/
    Browser->>Django: GET /suppliers/ + session cookie / JWT header

    Django->>Django: Validate session / JWT
    alt Token invalid or expired
        Django-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /login/
    else Token valid
        Django->>Django: Load request.user from token
        Django->>Django: Check LoginRequiredMixin
        Django->>DB: SELECT Supplier WHERE company=request.user.company
        Note over Django,DB: Tenant isolation enforced here
        DB-->>Django: Supplier queryset (own org only)
        Django-->>Browser: Render suppliers list
    end

    %% ─────────────────────────────────────
    %% LOGOUT FLOW
    %% ─────────────────────────────────────

    User->>Browser: Click logout
    Browser->>Django: POST /logout/
    Django->>Django: Invalidate session / blacklist JWT refresh token
    Django->>DB: INSERT AuditLog {action: logout, user, ip}
    Django-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /login/
```
